                   java.lang.Integer followerCount,

                   java.lang.String profileImageUrl)
        Creates a Twitter user data object to send to Appboy's servers. The SDK will only send fields which are non-null and non-empty.
        Parameters:
        twitterUserId - The Twitter user Id
        twitterHandle - The user's Twitter handle
        name - The user's name
        description - A description of the user
        followerCount - Number of Twitter users following this user
        followingCount - Number of Twitter users this user is following
        tweetCount - Number of Tweets by this user
        profileImageUrl - Link to profile image
